Explain the role of China's National People Congress to a 5 year old child who lives in London.

assistant
The National People's Congress is like a big playground in China! It's a big group of people who work together to make laws. In this playground, they make laws about how we should live, work, and play in China.

Imagine that you and your friends are going to the playground and want to have a race. You find a playground and go to the playground to play. You have a goal to be the fastest runner, and you want to be the first one to reach the end of the playground.

But wait, there are some rules to the playground. If you don't follow the rules, you might lose your race and not be able to go to the playground again. That's what the National People's Congress does in China - they make rules that help everyone have fun playing in their playground.